<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Wonderful Way</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Look around you: amazing creation!
 All the birds are singing His praise
 This world is made in a wonderful way

[V2]
 All the flowers and trees are declaring
 By the colors brightly displayed
 This world is made in a wonderful way

[V3]
 This is the marvelous way
 He gives joy everyday
 He will teach us to stay near to Him and
 Find the place that He's got for us
 To be part of what He has made
 Learning how to share love with all those around
 Whatever they say

[V4]
 I've seen babies with smiles on their faces
 Beaming innocent wonders of grace
 Each one is formed in a marvelous way

[V5]
 Every evening the stars are proclaiming
 The sun is shouting loudly each day
 This world is made in a wonderful way

[V6]
 This is the marvelous way
 He gives joy everyday
 He will teach us to stay near to Him and
 Find the place that He's got for us
 To be part of what He has made
 Learning how to share love with all those around
 Whatever they say

[V7]
 Look around you: amazing creation!
 The love of God overflows everywhere
 This world is formed in a marvelous way

[V8]
 Laughing, rejoicing and talking
 Each one is going his own chosen way
 True love is what we all need
 All will be complete in Him

[V9]
 Look around you: amazing creation!
 All the birds are singing His praise
 This world is made in a wonderful way
 This world was made by God alone
 Oh Yeah!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1926</hymn_number>
<author>Livingospel</author>
</song>